%%{init: {'theme':'base', 'themeVariables': { 'primaryColor':'#f8f9fa','primaryTextColor':'#212529','primaryBorderColor':'#adb5bd','lineColor':'#6c757d','secondaryColor':'#e9ecef','tertiaryColor':'#dee2e6','background':'transparent'}}}%%
graph TB
